 ('1042', '862', 'en_us', 'Choose a Suitable Location', '', '<h3>Some Factors to Consider</h3>\r\n\r\n<ol><li>What kind of location best suites your target customers (who walks by and who comes to visit the neighborhood)?&nbsp;</li><li>How much space do you need?</li><li>What kind of space will you need? Will you need special needs around&nbsp;plumbing,&nbsp;power, kitchens,&nbsp;etc.&nbsp;</li><li>What are the lease terms?</li><li>What can you afford to pay?</li><li>How much parking do you need?</li></ol>\r\n\r\n<p>We recommend that you have a strong&nbsp;understanding of&nbsp;the business, zoning/planning, and building permitting needs of your location before you sign your lease.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>There are several resources to help you find a business location in Oakland, including city staff, commercial brokers, website listings, and shopping district leaders.&nbsp;The City of Oakland Business Assistance Center can provide market analysis on neighborhood profiles, demographic reports, and more.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><br></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'info', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'hide', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-27 21:38:44', '2016-03-03 02:12:23', '72ed56e5-443b-4c09-815b-90a312bedc15'),
 ('1052', '872', 'en_us', 'Obtain a Zoning Clearance Permit', 'A zoning clearance permit is required if you plan to operate your business in Oakland', '<p>If you plan to operate a business in Oakland (including a home office), you will need to obtain a zoning permit called a&nbsp;<strong>Zoning Clearance</strong>. You do not need a&nbsp;<strong>Zoning Clearance</strong>&nbsp;if your business is located outside of Oakland or if your business activity is a rental property operator. The Zoning Clearance is granted if your business is allowed in the proposed location. In some instances, ahead of obtaining a Zoning Clearance, a proposed business activity must also go through a special&nbsp;<strong>Conditional Use Permit&nbsp;</strong>process to determine whether the activity will be allowed.&nbsp;<br></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Zoning Clearance is a one-time permit that is good as long as the nature of your business remains the same and in the same location. You will need this zoning permit before applying for your business tax certificate.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>You may obtain additional information about zoning permits and regulations via the&nbsp;<strong>Zoning Hotline</strong>&nbsp;(telephone), the&nbsp;<strong>Online Zoning Request Form</strong>&nbsp;or by visiting the&nbsp;<strong>Permit Counter. Zoning Clearances</strong>&nbsp;and other zoning permit applications are available online, but must be submitted and paid for in person at the Permit Counter.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>Businesses Located in the&nbsp;Port Area</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Any development or construction in the Port Area of Oakland (seaport, airport, or Oakland Airport Business Park)&nbsp;must be approved by the Port prior to start of work, and prior to submittal for a City of Oakland&nbsp;building permit.&nbsp;Submit a completed <a href=\"http://www.portofoakland.com/pdf/opportunities/permit_application2016.pdf\">application</a> and a project description to Joe Marsh, Port Permit Coordinator, 530 Water Street, Oakland, jmarsh@portoakland.com</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'info', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'hide', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-27 21:55:26', '2016-03-03 02:12:23', '60c8af2e-6a49-4561-ac9b-6a4b128f11a2'),
 ('1062', '882', 'en_us', 'Get Help Creating a Business Plan', 'Templates, classes, and advisors for creating a business plan', '<p>Before you get your license, find a location, or buy supplies or stock, it\'s important&nbsp;to plan out your business to&nbsp;project how much you will need and how much you will make over the next few years.&nbsp;This can prevent you from making big mistakes, going into credit card debt and&nbsp;other difficult situations. &nbsp;<br></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Templates of Business Plans:</strong><br></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://www.score.org/resources/business-planning-financial-statements-template-gallery\">SCORE</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.sbdcnet.org/small-business-information-center/business-plans\">SBDC</a>&nbsp;-&nbsp;<em>organized by type of&nbsp;business</em></li><li><a href=\"https://www.sba.gov/writing-business-plan\">SBA</a></li></ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Local Business Plan Classes and Advisors:&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul><li><a href=\"http://acsbdc.org/\">Alameda County SBDC</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.eastbayscore.org/\">SCORE&nbsp;East Bay Chapter</a></li><li><a href=\"http://anewamerica.org/index.php/program-highlight/160-announcing-new-business-development-classes-in-the-east-south-bay\">AnewAmerica</a>&nbsp;<em>- focused on&nbsp;immigrant and minority entrepreneurs</em></li></ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>While working on your Business Plan, the City of Oakland\'s&nbsp;business development staff can help you learn more about your potential market.&nbsp;To request assistance on market analysis from the City staff, please&nbsp;complete a <a href=\"http://oaklandbusinesscenter.com/request.html\">BAC Assistance Request form</a> to learn more about:<br></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul><li>Neighborhood profiles</li><li>Demographic reports</li><li>Industry sector reports</li><li>Traffic counts</li><li>Sales tax trends</li><li>Local taxes and costs</li><li>Labor force information</li><li>Major employer information</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'info', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'hide', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-27 22:12:25', '2016-03-03 02:12:24', 'a15b1bfd-4800-4acf-9c94-3e9eae4d538f'),
