 ('1552', '1712', 'en_us', 'Check Zoning Regulations for Your Property', '', '<p>Once you have a couple of location options, you should check&nbsp;the planning map and zoning code&nbsp;to see if your location outright permitted, conditionally permitted or not permitted.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This step can be complicated depending on the type of business. Unless you are familiar with planning and zoning regulations, we recommend you talk with a planner at the City of&nbsp;Oakland.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'info', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'hide', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-02-10 23:20:08', '2016-03-03 02:12:33', '7a241ded-d1fe-4cb7-9724-d8d00f588f0d'),
