 ('3832', '62', 'es', 'Apply for a Disabled Parking Blue Zone', '', '<h3>Disabled Parking&nbsp;Blue Zone&nbsp;Program</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>A Blue Zone&nbsp;provides on-street parking for people with disabilities. The Blue Zone&nbsp;has a painted blue curb with a posted sign.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Residents and businesses can request Blue Zones&nbsp;from the Disabled Parking Zone program.<br>The City does not install “Blue Zones&nbsp;for paratransit drop-off and pick-up.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>To learn more, please read the Policy summaries below.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><br><a href=\"http://www2.oaklandnet.com/oakca1/groups/pwa/documents/policy/oak051830.pdf\">Residential Blue Zone Policy Summary<br></a><a href=\"http://www2.oaklandnet.com/oakca1/groups/pwa/documents/policy/oak051829.pdf\">Non-Residential Blue Zone Policy Summary</a></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'information', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-03 02:12:05', '2016-03-03 02:12:05', '6fd3bbe2-c18f-466c-9a94-0aa74ce18501'),
