 ('4172', '272', 'es', 'Find a City Owned Parking Garage', '', '<p>To find a City-owned garage or lot, check out the Oakland Parking Map above.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please contact the parking operator if you have questions about a specific garage.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>You can find contact information on the map below by clicking on the “P” linked to the garage.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>A limited number of monthly parking permits are available at some metered outdoor lots. If you have questions about these permits, please call (510) 238-6154.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'information', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-03 02:12:12', '2016-03-03 02:12:12', '50332269-4bb2-4457-b1ca-f029b6950fc7'),
