 ('4352', '382', 'es', 'Employee Assistance Program (EAP)', '', '<p>The employee assistance program (EAP) provides City of Oakland employees and their families with free resources. These benefits help address personal and work-related problems. City employees and their families may use these services confidentially.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"examples-of-eap-services\">Examples of EAP Services</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>In-person counseling</li>\r\n  <li>Substance abuse treatment</li>\r\n  <li>Free legal advice and referrals</li>\r\n  <li>Financial services</li>\r\n  <li>Services for your family</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Claremont EAP manages the EAP for the City of Oakland. Request services by contacting their counselors.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"how-to-request-eap-services\">How to Request EAP Services</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr><th>\r\nPhone</th><th>Online</th></tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr><td style=\"background-color:white\">\r\nClaremont EAP: (800) 834-3773\r\n</td><td>\r\n[Enroll online](http://claremonteap.personaladvantage.com/gateway.jsp?SingleSignIn:refid=10349826.)\r\n</td></tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'information', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-03 02:12:17', '2016-03-03 02:12:17', '6b53cfd6-0198-4fde-8b8d-603c4a5ace41'),
