 ('4632', '692', 'es', 'Pick Up Sandbags & Plastic Sheeting for Your Neighborhood', 'The City of Oakland Offers Sandbags & Plastic Sheeting to Residents and Businesses', '<p>The City of Oakland will provide emergency sandbags and plastic sheeting when heavy rains are forecast. Each Oakland resident and business owner may pickup sandbags (up to 10)&nbsp;and plastic sheeting (up to 20 feet) at the following locations, as long as supplies last.&nbsp;Bring your ID to prove residency. Be prepared to fill your own if needed.<br>&nbsp;<br><strong>Municipal Service Center</strong>, 7101 Edgewater Drive<br>Monday – Friday, 8 a.m. – 4 p.m.<br>Saturday & Sunday, 8 a.m. – 4:30 p.m.<br>After Hours (at entry gate) 4:30 p.m. – 8 a.m.<br>&nbsp;<br><strong>Drainage Services Facility</strong>, 5921 Shepherd Canyon<br>Monday – Friday, 8 a.m. – 4 p.m.<br>After Hours (at entry gate) 4:30 p.m. – 8 a.m.</p><p><strong>Need more bags?&nbsp;</strong>You can pick up bags at your local hardware, garden or home improvement stores.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Want to learn how to make a sandbag?</strong> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MRylOmhwgX8\" target=\"true\">Watch this video.</a></p><p><strong>Want to learn how to use plastic sheeting?</strong> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oKxRIr-qaV4\" target=\"true\">Watch this video.</a></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'info', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'hide', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-03 02:12:22', '2016-03-03 02:12:22', 'ad6dc4bc-b659-4650-9e87-e2121f1132e1'),
