 ('4832', '932', 'es', 'Check Your Location with Utility Companies', '', '<h2>Local Utility&nbsp;Providers</h2><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.pge.com/\">PG&E</a> (Electricity and Gas)</li><li><a href=\"http://www.ebmud.com/\">EBMUD</a> (Water and Sewage)</li><li><a href=\"https://www.acgov.org/aceh/\">Alameda Country Environmental Health</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.xfinity.com/\">Comcast</a> (Internet)</li></ul><p> Make sure to contact your utility providers&nbsp;as soon as you find your location to get everything&nbsp;in order.&nbsp; Depending on the services you need, your building may require&nbsp;upgrades which take additional time and money.&nbsp;It is recommended that you get your requests in early.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'info', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'hide', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-03 02:12:25', '2016-03-03 02:12:25', '238ff168-e5dc-4819-b45e-4109039da510'),
 ('4842', '932', 'zh', 'Check Your Location with Utility Companies', '', '<h2>Local Utility&nbsp;Providers</h2><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.pge.com/\">PG&E</a> (Electricity and Gas)</li><li><a href=\"http://www.ebmud.com/\">EBMUD</a> (Water and Sewage)</li><li><a href=\"https://www.acgov.org/aceh/\">Alameda Country Environmental Health</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.xfinity.com/\">Comcast</a> (Internet)</li></ul><p> Make sure to contact your utility providers&nbsp;as soon as you find your location to get everything&nbsp;in order.&nbsp; Depending on the services you need, your building may require&nbsp;upgrades which take additional time and money.&nbsp;It is recommended that you get your requests in early.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'info', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'hide', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-03 02:12:25', '2016-03-03 02:12:25', '8e3b3f74-4da8-42f2-8532-1160a746ce8b'),
 ('4852', '942', 'es', 'Register Your Business Name', 'File a fictitious business name statement', '<p>If you intend to name your firm anything other than your own name, you must file a Fictitious Business Name Statement at the Alameda County Clerk\'s Office.&nbsp;This generally costs $30.&nbsp;You can download an application online (PDF), pick one up in person, or have one mailed to you.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>You may pay by cash, debit/ATM, check (personal, company, bank, cashier\'s or traveler\'s) or money order.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h4>Ficitious Business Name Applications & Info Hours</h4>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Monday - Friday<br>8:30 am - 4:30 pm</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h4>Turning in Your Application by Mail</h4>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Please be sure to send the original and&nbsp;3 copies&nbsp;of the form and a self-addressed stamped envelope to ensure a prompt return of your copies. Payment for additional certified copies are $2.00 per copy.&nbsp;\r\nYou may pay by check (personal, company, bank, or cashiers), money order or traveler\'s checks. Out of country payments must be made in U.S. dollars. Credit cards are&nbsp;notaccepted for mail orders.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'info', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'hide', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-03 02:12:25', '2016-03-03 