 ('5252', '1802', 'es', 'Schedule Your Inspections with Public Works', '', '<p>Public works issues permits regarding construction around the area of your property including:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol><li>CGS&nbsp;(curb, gutter, sidewalk, encroachment)</li><li>X (excavations)</li><li>SL (Sewer Lateral)</li><li>P-Job (Infrastructure for larger projects around landscaping)</li></ol><p><br></p>\r\n\r\n<p>During stages of construction, you will need to schedule inspections with the Public Works department to make sure your space complies with these permits.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Public Works Department Hours</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Monday through Friday, 8:00AM to 5:00PM<br></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'info', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'hide', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-03 02:12:34', '2016-03-03 02:12:34', 'cec5fbdd-ad77-447c-a28b-607499aaa69c'),
