 ('5332', '1932', 'es', 'Get Financing for Your Business', '', '<p>If you need money to start or grow your business, it is important to think about what type of financing best fits your business and aligns with your values. Different financing options include:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol><li>Loans from Community&nbsp;Organizations & Institutions</li><li>Loans from Community Banks</li><li>0% Loans from Peer-to-Peer Platforms</li><li>Crowdfunding – Reward/Donation-Based</li><li>Crowdfunding – Investment-Based</li><li>Angel Investors</li><li>Impact Investment Funds</li></ol>\r\n\r\n<p>For more information and programs within these&nbsp;financing options, please refer to the Small Business Association\'s (SBA) <a href=\"http://cdn.localon.com/upload-4722960365254482686.pdf\">Good Local Money Guide</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2>Popular Oakland Financing Programs</h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Oakland Business Development Center (OBDC)</strong><br><em>Small business&nbsp;loans ranging from&nbsp;$10,000 to&nbsp;$25,000<br></em>825 Washington St.,&nbsp;Ste. 200<br>Oakland, CA 94607<br>(510) 830-3275</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kiva Zip</strong><br><em>Peer to Peer donations for loans up to $25,000<br></em>875 Howard St.<br>San Francisco, CA 94103<br>(713) 924-8170</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><br></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'info', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'hide', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-03 02:12:36', '2016-03-03 02:12:36', '75ffa82c-1e02-409c-9515-b5900329b507'),
 ('5342', '1932', 'zh', 'Get Financing for Your Business', '', '<p>If you need money to start or grow your business, it is important to think about what type of financing best fits your business and aligns with your values. Different financing options include:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol><li>Loans from Community&nbsp;Organizations & Institutions</li><li>Loans from Community Banks</li><li>0% Loans from Peer-to-Peer Platforms</li><li>Crowdfunding – Reward/Donation-Based</li><li>Crowdfunding – Investment-Based</li><li>Angel Investors</li><li>Impact Investment Funds</li></ol>\r\n\r\n<p>For more information and programs within these&nbsp;financing options, please refer to the Small Business Association\'s (SBA) <a href=\"http://cdn.localon.com/upload-4722960365254482686.pdf\">Good Local Money Guide</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2>Popular Oakland Financing Programs</h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Oakland Business Development Center (OBDC)</strong><br><em>Small business&nbsp;loans ranging from&nbsp;$10,000 to&nbsp;$25,000<br></em>825 Washington St.,&nbsp;Ste. 200<br>Oakland, CA 94607<br>(510) 830-3275</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kiva Zip</strong><br><em>Peer to Peer donations for loans up to $25,000<br></em>875 Howard St.<br>San Francisco, CA 94103<br>(713) 924-8170</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><br></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'info', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'hide', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-03 02:12:36', '2016-03-03 02:12:36', 'b042157b-35b5-4418-9fb8-0473bbd339cc'),
