 ('7422', '3682', 'en_us', 'Find Shelters for the Homeless', '', '<h2>Who Do We Assist?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Individual and families who have exhausted all other resources including family and friends.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>More About Our Referrals</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.edenir.org/\">Eden I&R</a></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Eden Information &&nbsp;Referral&nbsp;provides information and referrals via a toll free hotline that is updated twice daily with local shelters with openings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2-1-1 operates 24 hours a day, 7 days a week with multi-lingual capabilities.<br></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.ci.berkeley.ca.us/ContentDisplay.aspx?id=5554\">Berkeley Shelter Hotline</a>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The Berkeley&nbsp;Shelter Hotline&nbsp;helps individual <strong class=\"redactor-inline-converted\">without children or partners </strong>find beds at shelters.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong class=\"redactor-inline-converted\">Hours:</strong>&nbsp;Monday - Friday 9:00 a.m. - 12 noon and 1:00 p.m. - 4:00 p.m.<br><strong>Location:</strong>&nbsp;1901 Fairview Street, Berkeley, CA 94703</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>North County Coordinated Access System</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>For families (people&nbsp;with dependents), the&nbsp;North County Coordinated Access System provides case management services, housing search assistance, and housing&nbsp;subsidies.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'info', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'hide', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-04-12 21:48:07', '2016-04-12 21:49:29', '53dcea2f-556f-4c15-a0af-627143c66b93'),
