 ('652', '6', '3', '1', 'en_us', '29', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Pay a Parking Ticket\",\"slug\":\"pay-a-parking-ticket\",\"postDate\":1449259680,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"122\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>You have 21 days after the date the ticket was written to make a payment.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2 id=\\\"ways-to-pay\\\">Pay by Phone<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Parking Citation Assistance Center<\\/strong><br>Phone: (800) 500-6484<br>Please have your&nbsp;credit card on hand&nbsp;(Visa, Mastercard, Discover or American Express)<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Pay by&nbsp;Mail or&nbsp;In Person<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Parking Citation Assistance Center<\\/strong><br>250 Frank H. Ogawa Plaza, Suite 6300 Oakland, CA 94612<br>Mondays, Tuesdays, Thursdays and Fridays from 9 a.m. to 4:30 p.m.<br>Wednesdays from 9:30 a.m. to 4:30 p.m.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Additional In Person Locations<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Parking ticket payment kiosks<\\/strong><br>250 Frank H. Ogawa Plaza<br>Monday through Friday from 8:30 a.m. to 5 p.m.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Eastmont Police Substation<\\/strong><br>2651 73rd Avenue<br>Monday through Saturday from 8:00 a.m. to 4 p.m.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2 id=\\\"by-mail\\\">Pay by Mail<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Mail your parking ticket&nbsp;and the full payment to:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Parking Citation Assistance Center<\\/strong><br>250 Frank H. Ogawa Plaza, Suite 6300<br>Oakland, CA 94612<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Refund Request Form<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>If you feel you are due a refund for overpayment for a parking ticket associated with your license plate, please complete and return a Refund Request Form.\\r\\nClick here to download the Refund Request Form.\\r\\nProvide proof of payment as detailed on the form.\\r\\nPlease allow four to six weeks for processing.\\r\\nCompleted forms and proof of payment can be submitted by mail, in person or by fax.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3 id=\\\"mailin-person\\\">Mail\\/In Person<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Parking Citation Assistance Center<br>250 Frank H. Ogawa Plaza, Suite 6300 Oakland, CA 94612<br>Mondays, Tuesdays, Thursdays and Fridays from 9 a.m. to 4:30 p.m.<br>Wednesdays from 9:30 a.m. to 4:30 p.m.<br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Additional References<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/oakland-beta.herokuapp.com\\/services\\/parking\\/find-parking\\/costs-of-common-parking-violations#entry:332\\\">Costs of Common Parking Violations<\\/a><\\/li><li><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www2.oaklandnet.com\\/oakca1\\/groups\\/ceda\\/documents\\/marketingmaterial\\/oak044797.pdf\\\">Complete roster of parking violation fines from the OMC and California Vehicle Code<\\/a><\\/li><li><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/library.municode.com\\/index.aspx?clientId=16308&stateId=5&stateName=California\\\">Oakland Municipal Code about parking violations<\\/a><\\/li><li><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.leginfo.ca.gov\\/cgi-bin\\/calawquery?codesection=veh\\\">California Vehicle Code<\\/a><\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"5\":\"https:\\/\\/prodpci.etimspayments.com\\/pbw\\/include\\/oakland\\/input.jsp\",\"3\":\"Pay your ticket online\",\"4\":\"\"}}', '2015-12-19 01:02:11', '2015-12-19 01:02:11', 'ce924278-dc20-4f71-a686-f4d2ef2a4bf1'),
 ('662', '132', '3', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Contest a Parking Ticket\",\"slug\":\"contest-a-parking-ticket\",\"postDate\":1450478580,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"122\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<h2>What You Need to Know<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n  <li>Please wait 48 hours from the time of issuance to ensure your citation is entered into the online system.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>It may take handwritten tickets up to two weeks to be entered into the online system.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>You must contest your ticket within 21 days of the date of issuance.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>You\\u2019ll need to upload up to three documents that provide evidence to support your written testimony.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2 id=\\\"ways-to-contest-a-ticket\\\">Ways to Contest a Ticket<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><a href=\\\"\\\">Download and complete the <\\/a><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www2.oaklandnet.com\\/oakca1\\/groups\\/cityadministrator\\/documents\\/form\\/oak041670.pdf\\\">Contest Form<\\/a> or write a letter of explanation for contesting your citation.\\r\\nPlease include your name, address, telephone number, current mailing address and parking ticket citation number.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Keep a copy of your ticket for your records.\\r\\nReturn your Contest Form or letter, along with the original parking ticket and additional documents:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>In person or by mail<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Parking Citation Assistance Center<br>250 Frank H. Ogawa Plaza, Suite 6300<br>Oakland, CA 94612<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>By fax<\\/strong><\\/p><p><strong><\\/strong>(510) 986-2699<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Contesting a parking ticket by email is not possible at this time.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3 id=\\\"what-happens-next\\\">What Happens Next<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n  <li>The Parking Citation Assistance Center investigates your ticket.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>You will be notified of the decision by mail.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>If the ticket is upheld, you will have 21 days to pay your ticket or request an Administrative Hearing.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>If you contested a parking ticket and you are not satisfied with the decision, you can <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/oakland-beta.herokuapp.com\\/services\\/parking\\/find-parking\\/request-an-administrative-hearing#entry:182\\\">request an Administrative Hearing<\\/a>.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\",\"5\":\"https:\\/\\/wmq.etimspayments.com\\/pbw\\/include\\/oakland\\/dispute_request.jsp.\",\"3\":\"Contest your parking ticket online\",\"4\":\"\"}}', '2015-12-19 01:06:02', '2015-12-19 01:06:02', '5c873ba8-3377-4794-b28b-8e807ab530ee'),
