 ('1672', '942', '3', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Register Your Business Name\",\"slug\":\"register-your-business-name\",\"postDate\":1453934148,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"922\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>If you intend to name your firm anything other than your own name, you must file a Fictitious Business Name Statement at the Alameda County Clerk\'s Office.<br>This generally costs $30.&nbsp;You can download an application online (PDF), pick one up in person, or have one mailed to you.<br><\\/p><h3>Turning in your Application<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4>In Person<\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You may pay by cash, debit\\/ATM, check (personal, company, bank, cashier\'s or traveler\'s) or money order.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Ficitious Business Name Applications & Info<br>Alameda County Clerk\'s Office<br>1106 Madison Street, Room 136<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Monday - Friday<br>8:30 am - 4:30 pm<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4>By Mail<\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Please be sure to send the original and&nbsp;3 copies&nbsp;of the form and a self-addressed stamped envelope to ensure a prompt return of your copies. Payment for additional certified copies are $2.00 per copy.&nbsp;\\r\\nYou may pay by check (personal, company, bank, or cashiers), money order or traveler\'s checks. Out of country payments must be made in U.S. dollars. Credit cards are&nbsp;notaccepted for mail orders. Send request to:&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p><p>Alameda County Clerk-Recorder\'s Office<br>1106 Madison Street<br>Oakland, CA 94607<\\/p>\",\"5\":\"http:\\/\\/www.acgov.org\\/forms\\/auditor\\/275-321.pdf\",\"92\":\"1 (510) 272-6363\",\"3\":\"Download the online application\",\"4\":\"\"}}', '2016-01-27 22:35:49', '2016-01-27 22:35:49', '2ed759fc-2203-4ed8-b163-0c39d5768dc8'),
