 ('2212', '1052', '3', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Get Consultation on What Permits You Will Need\",\"slug\":\"get-consultation-on-what-permits-you-will-need\",\"postDate\":1454544593,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"992\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>Figuring out what permits you may need for your business can be a complicated process. We recommend talking to a business permitting specialist either in person or on the phone.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Visit or Call Us<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Oakland Business Assistance Center<br>270 Frank H. Ogawa Plaza<br>1&nbsp;(510)&nbsp;238-7952<br>Monday \\u2013 Friday&nbsp;<br>9:00 a.m. \\u2013 5:00 p.m.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Talk with a Specialist<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Keira Williams<br><\\/strong><em>Retail<\\/em><br>(510) 238-3853<br><a href=\\\"mailto:kwilliams@oaklandnet.com\\\">kwilliams@oaklandnet.com<\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Marisa Raya<\\/strong><br><em>Technology<\\/em><br>(510) 238-6230&nbsp;<br><a href=\\\"mailto:mraya@oaklandnet.com\\\">mraya@oaklandnet.com<\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Steve Lautze<\\/strong><br><em>Green, Recycle-based, or Alternative Energy<\\/em><br>(510) 238-4973<br><a href=\\\"mailto:slautze@oaklandnet.com\\\">slautze@oaklandnet.com<\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Margot Lederer Prado<\\/strong><br><em>Manufacturing and Industrial Uses, Arts\\/Engineering\\/Design, Food and Beverage, Healthcare and Wellness<\\/em><br>(510) 238-6766 &nbsp;&nbsp;<br><a href=\\\"mailto:mprado@oaklandnet.com\\\">mprado@oaklandnet.com<\\/a><\\/p>\",\"5\":\"\",\"92\":\"\",\"3\":\"\",\"4\":\"\"}}', '2016-02-04 00:09:53', '2016-02-04 00:09:53', '62d62c67-4619-4c16-9c26-d00d928a0637'),
 ('2222', '1062', '3', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Preparing Your Space\",\"slug\":\"preparing-your-space\",\"postDate\":1454544753,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"742\",\"fields\":{\"4\":\"Including Fire Department Compliance, Building Compliance, and Inspections\"}}', '2016-02-04 00:12:33', '2016-02-04 00:12:33', 'fed7f324-4417-4138-888d-a846a4bc5d8b'),
 ('2232', '872', '3', '1', 'en_us', '5', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Obtain a Zoning Clearance Permit\",\"slug\":\"obtain-a-zoning-permit\",\"postDate\":1453931700,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"922\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>If you plan to operate a business in Oakland (including a home office), you will need to obtain a zoning permit called a&nbsp;<strong>Zoning Clearance<\\/strong>. You do not need a&nbsp;<strong>Zoning Clearance<\\/strong>&nbsp;if your business is located outside of Oakland or if your business activity is a rental property operator. The Zoning Clearance is granted if your business is allowed in the proposed location. In some instances, ahead of obtaining a Zoning Clearance, a proposed business activity must also go through a special&nbsp;<strong>Conditional Use Permit&nbsp;<\\/strong>process to determine whether the activity will be allowed.&nbsp;<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The Zoning Clearance is a one-time permit that is good as long as the nature of your business remains the same and in the same location. You will need this zoning permit before applying for your business tax certificate.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You may obtain additional information about zoning permits and regulations via the&nbsp;<strong>Zoning Hotline<\\/strong>&nbsp;(telephone), the&nbsp;<strong>Online Zoning Request Form<\\/strong>&nbsp;or by visiting the&nbsp;<strong>Permit Counter. Zoning Clearances<\\/strong>&nbsp;and other zoning permit applications are available online, but must be submitted and paid for in person at the Permit Counter.<\\/p>\",\"5\":\"http:\\/\\/www2.oaklandnet.com\\/oakca1\\/groups\\/ceda\\/documents\\/agenda\\/oak040732.pdf\",\"92\":\"1 (510) 238-3911\",\"3\":\"Download the zoning clearance application\",\"4\":\"A zoning clearance permit is required if you plan to operate your business in Oakland\"}}', '2016-02-04 00:20:45', '2016-02-04 00:20:45', 'e138bd17-1b87-4de2-bf26-c8892bde99fd'),
 ('2242', '882', '3', '442', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Consider and Prepare your Business Plan\",\"slug\":\"before-you-start\",\"postDate\":1453932720,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"742\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<h4>Creating a Business Plan:<\\/h4><p>Business Plan&nbsp;Templates and advisors&nbsp;are available on&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.score.org\\/resources\\/business-planning-financial-statements-template-gallery\\\">SCORE<\\/a>,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.sbdcnet.org\\/small-business-information-center\\/business-plans\\\">SBDC<\\/a> (templates&nbsp;by business type), and&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.sba.gov\\/writing-business-plan\\\">SBA<\\/a><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\",\"5\":\"\",\"92\":\"\",\"3\":\"\",\"4\":\"Learn if starting a business is right for you, if there\'s a market, and how to create a business plan\"}}', '2016-02-04 19:33:33', '2016-02-04 19:33:33', 'e1f553cf-89ae-48ff-8b43-986bfe9f421a'),
 ('2252', '882', '3', '442', 'en_us', '4', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Create your Business Plan\",\"slug\":\"before-you-start\",\"postDate\":1453932720,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"742\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>Before you get your license, find a location, or buy supplies or stock, it\'s a good idea to plan out your business. The plan should&nbsp;project how much you will need and how much you will make over the next few years.&nbsp;This can prevent you from making big mistakes, going into credit card debt or other difficult situations. &nbsp;<br><\\/p><p><strong>Templates of Business Plans:<\\/strong><br><\\/p><ul><li><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.score.org\\/resources\\/business-planning-financial-statements-template-gallery\\\">SCORE<\\/a><\\/li><li><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.sbdcnet.org\\/small-business-information-center\\/business-plans\\\">SBDC<\\/a>&nbsp;-&nbsp;<em>organized by type of&nbsp;business)<\\/em><\\/li><li><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.sba.gov\\/writing-business-plan\\\">SBA<\\/a><\\/li><\\/ul><p><strong>Local Business Plan Classes and Advisors:&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/p><ul><li><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/acsbdc.org\\/\\\">Alameda County SBDC<\\/a><\\/li><li><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.eastbayscore.org\\/\\\">SCORE&nbsp;East Bay Chapter<\\/a><\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"5\":\"\",\"92\":\"\",\"3\":\"\",\"4\":\"Templates, classes, and advisors for creating a business plan\"}}', '2016-02-04 21:28:53', '2016-02-04 21:28:53', 'a5315bf8-57bd-4e8b-acd1-f162dd543bb8'),
