<br>250 Frank H. Ogawa Plaza, Suite 6300 Oakland, CA 94612<br>Mondays, Tuesdays, Thursdays and Fridays from 9 a.m. to 4:30 p.m.<br>Wednesdays from 9:30 a.m. to 4:30 p.m.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Additional References<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/beta.oaklandca.gov\\/index.php?p=services\\/parking\\/find-parking\\/costs-of-common-parking-violations#entry:332:url\\\">Costs of Common Parking Violations<\\/a><\\/li><li><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www2.oaklandnet.com\\/oakca1\\/groups\\/ceda\\/documents\\/marketingmaterial\\/oak044797.pdf\\\">Complete roster of parking violation fines from the OMC and California Vehicle Code<\\/a><\\/li><li><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/library.municode.com\\/index.aspx?clientId=16308&stateId=5&stateName=California\\\">Oakland Municipal Code about parking violations<\\/a><\\/li><li><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.leginfo.ca.gov\\/cgi-bin\\/calawquery?codesection=veh\\\">California Vehicle Code<\\/a><\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"312\":{\"1372\":{\"type\":\"onlineLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"linkTitle\":\"Pay your ticket online\",\"linkUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/prodpci.etimspayments.com\\/pbw\\/include\\/oakland\\/input.jsp\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"1\"}},\"1382\":{\"type\":\"phoneNumber\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"number\":\"1 (800) 500-6484\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"\"}},\"1392\":{\"type\":\"physicalAddress\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"physicalAddressTitle\":\"Mail In or Pay in Person\",\"address\":\"<p><strong>Parking Citation Assistance Center<\\/strong><br>250 Frank H. Ogawa Plaza, Suite 6300<br>Oakland, CA 94612<br><\\/p>\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"\"}}},\"5\":\"https:\\/\\/prodpci.etimspayments.com\\/pbw\\/include\\/oakland\\/input.jsp\",\"92\":\"\",\"3\":\"Pay your ticket online\",\"4\":\"\"}}', '2016-02-10 00:00:36', '2016-02-10 00:00:36', 'bc9c2ffa-4dd5-4cae-a39a-28c371e9d127');
