t-an-administrative-hearing#entry:182:url\\\">request an Administrative Hearing<\\/a>.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\",\"312\":{\"1402\":{\"type\":\"onlineLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"linkTitle\":\"Contest online\",\"linkUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/wmq.etimspayments.com\\/pbw\\/include\\/oakland\\/dispute_request.jsp.\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"1\"}},\"1412\":{\"type\":\"phoneNumber\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"number\":\"(510) 986-2699\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"\"}},\"1422\":{\"type\":\"physicalAddress\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"physicalAddressTitle\":\"In Person or By Mail\",\"address\":\"<p><strong>Parking Citation Assistance Center<\\/strong><br>250 Frank H. Ogawa Plaza, Suite 6300<br>Oakland, CA 94612<\\/p>\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"\"}}},\"5\":\"\",\"92\":\"\",\"3\":\"\",\"4\":\"\"}}', '2016-02-10 00:04:41', '2016-02-10 00:04:41', 'b43ca792-45ad-4860-b21f-27a145246a97'),
 ('2972', '312', '3', '1', 'en_us', '4', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Apply for Disabled Persons Parking Placards and Plates\",\"slug\":\"apply-for-disabled-persons-parking-placards-and-plates\",\"postDate\":1450483560,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"52\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>You may qualify for a Disabled Person placard or license plates if you have one or more of the conditions below.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n  <li>Inability to use one or more lower limbs, or both hands<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>Diagnosed disease that impairs or interferes with mobility<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>Severe disability that leaves you unable to move without an assistive device<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>Documented problems with your eyesight such as lower-vision or partial-sightedness<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>The City of Oakland does not issue Disabled Person placards or license plates<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3 id=\\\"illegal-use-of-disabled-parking\\\">Illegal Use of Disabled Parking<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Only the disabled driver issued the placard or plates can use the parking placard or plates.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>A driver that does any of the actions below can receive tickets and fines.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n  <li>Lend your Disabled Person placard to someone else<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>Use someone else\\u2019s Disabled Person placard<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>Have or display a fake Disabled Person placard or license plates<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Report illegal use of Disabled Person placards and plates. Please call Parking Enforcement at (510) 238-3099.<\\/p>\",\"312\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"onlineLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"linkTitle\":\"Apply with the California DMV\",\"linkUrl\":\"http:\\/\\/www.dmv.ca.gov\\/pubs%2Fbrochures\\/fast_facts\\/ffvr07.htm\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"1\"}}},\"5\":\"\",\"92\":\"\",\"3\":\"\",\"4\":\"\"}}', '2016-02-10 00:05:18', '2016-02-10 00:05:18', 'ea405cbb-8b1c-449a-91e8-f939d3cd4455'),
 ('2982', '152', '3', '1', 'en_us', '4', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Set up a Parking Citation Alert\",\"slug\":\"create-your-own-parking-citation-alert\",\"postDate\":1450480080,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"252\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>Parking citation alerts provide notifications to help manage your parking needs and avoid unnecessary penalties. When you create an account, it will alert you so you receive notifications about:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n  <li>\\r\\n    <p>When a new citation is issued to your vehicle<\\/p>\\r\\n  <\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>\\r\\n    <p>Before a penalty are applied<\\/p>\\r\\n  <\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>\\r\\n    <p>After a mail-in payment is applied<\\/p>\\r\\n  <\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>\\r\\n    <p>About upcoming hearings<\\/p>\\r\\n  <\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>\\r\\n    <p>Before you become \\u201cBoot Eligible\\u201d<\\/p>\\r\\n  <\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>\\r\\n    <p>Upcoming Resident Parking Permit Renewal<\\/p>\\r\\n  <\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>\\r\\n    <p>City of Oakland Parking announcements<\\/p><\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"312\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"onlineLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"linkTitle\":\"Sign up for alerts\",\"linkUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/wmq1.etimspayments.com\\/pbw\\/include\\/vpportal\\/oakland\\/login_page.jsp\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"1\"}}},\"5\":\"\",\"92\":\"\",\"3\":\"\",\"4\":\"\"}}', '2016-02-10 00:06:55', '2016-02-10 00:06:55', '41f12973-6973-446a-8a27-4e9aacc5138b'),
 ('2992', '942', '3', '1', 'en_us', '9', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Register Your Business Name\",\"slug\":\"register-your-business-name\",\"postDate\":1453934100,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"922\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>If you intend to name your firm anything other than your own name, you must file a Fictitious Business Name Statement at the Alameda County Clerk\'s Office.&nbsp;This generally costs $30.&nbsp;You can download an application online (PDF), pick one up in person, or have one mailed to you.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You may pay by cash, debit\\/ATM, check (personal, company, bank, cashier\'s or traveler\'s) or money order.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4>Ficitious Business Name Applications & Info Hours<\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Monday - Friday<br>8:30 am - 4:30 pm<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4>Turning in Your Application by Mail<\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Please be sure to send the original and&nbsp;3 copies&nbsp;of the form and a self-addressed stamped envelope to ensure a prompt return of your copies. Payment for additional certified copies are $2.00 per copy.&nbsp;\\r\\nYou may pay by check (personal, company, bank, or cashiers), money order or traveler\'s checks. Out of country payments must be made in U.S. dollars. Credit cards are&nbsp;notaccepted for mail orders.<\\/p>\",\"312\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":