 ('3252', '182', '3', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Request an Administrative Hearing\",\"slug\":\"request-an-administrative-hearing\",\"postDate\":1450480560,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"252\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>If you contested a parking ticket and you are not satisfied with the decision, you can request an Administrative Hearing.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3 id=\\\"what-you-need-to-know\\\">What You Need to Know<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n  <li>Once you receive the decision from contesting your ticket, you have 21 days to schedule a hearing.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>You can request a hearing either in person or or by mail.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>You must pay a deposit equal to the amount of the fine before scheduling a hearing.<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3 id=\\\"what-happens-next\\\">What Happens Next<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n  <li>You will receive a notice by mail with the date and time of the hearing.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>All hearings are held Monday through Friday between 9 a.m. and 4 p.m.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>The hearing will be held at:<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Eastmont Mall Police Substation<\\/strong><br>2651 73rd Avenue, Upper Level<br>Oakland, CA<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>If you cannot attend your scheduled hearing, you have two options:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3 id=\\\"rescheduling-a-hearing\\\">Rescheduling a Hearing<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You have two options if you cannot attend the scheduled hearing:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Reschedule the hearing<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Call th