ave two options if you cannot attend the scheduled hearing:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Reschedule the hearing<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Call the Hearing Department at (510) 238-4484 at least five calendar days before the scheduled hearing.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Request a hearing by mail<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Send a letter detailing your dispute and include all the required documentation.<\\/p>\",\"312\":{\"1672\":{\"type\":\"phoneNumber\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"phoneNumberTitle\":\"Request By Phone\",\"number\":\"1 (800) 500-6484\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"1\"}},\"1662\":{\"type\":\"onlineLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"onlineTitle\":\"Get the Form\",\"linkTitle\":\"Download the Hearing Deposit Waiver Form\",\"linkUrl\":\"http:\\/\\/www2.oaklandnet.com\\/oakca1\\/groups\\/ceda\\/documents\\/marketingmaterial\\/oak044809.pdf\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"1\"}},\"1682\":{\"type\":\"physicalAddress\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"physicalAddressTitle\":\"Submit the Form (In Person or By Mail)\",\"address\":\"<p><strong>Parking Citation Assistance Center \\u2013 Hearing Dept.<\\/strong><br>250 Frank H. Ogawa Plaza, Suite 6300<br>Oakland, CA 94612<\\/p>\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"\"}}},\"4\":\"If you contested a parking ticket and you are not satisfied with the decision, you can request an Administrative Hearing either by phone or submitting the form in person or by mail.\"}}', '2016-02-10 21:44:43', '2016-02-10 21:44:43', '18c6a3c7-f7e2-45ac-8a16-4a0a88da26e3'),
 ('3312', '942', '3', '1', 'en_us', '11', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Register Your Business Name\",\"slug\":\"register-your-business-name\",\"postDate\":1453934100,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"922\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>If you intend to name your firm anything other than your own name, you must file a Fictitious Business Name Statement at the Alameda County Clerk\'s Office.&nbsp;This generally costs $30.&nbsp;You can download an application online (PDF), pick one up in person, or have one mailed to you.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You may pay by cash, debit\\/ATM, check (personal, company, bank, cashier\'s or traveler\'s) or money order.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4>Ficitious Business Name Applications & Info Hours<\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Monday - Friday<br>8:30 am - 4:30 pm<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4>Turning in Your Application by Mail<\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Please be sure to send the original and&nbsp;3 copies&nbsp;of the form and a self-addressed stamped envelope to ensure a prompt return of your copies. Payment for additional certified copies are $2.00 per copy.&nbsp;\\r\\nYou may pay by check (personal, company, bank, or cashiers), money order or traveler\'s checks. Out of country payments must be made in U.S. dollars. Credit cards are&nbsp;notaccepted for mail orders.<\\/p>\",\"312\":{\"1452\":{\"type\":\"onlineLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"onlineTitle\":\"Get the Form Online\",\"linkTitle\":\"Download the Fictitious Business Name Application\",\"linkUrl\":\"http:\\/\\/www.acgov.org\\/forms\\/auditor\\/275-321.pdf\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"1\"}},\"1472\":{\"type\":\"physicalAddress\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"physicalAddressTitle\":\"Turning in Your Application In Person or By Mail\",\"address\":\"<p><strong>Ficitious Business Name Applications & Info<\\/strong><br>Alameda County Clerk\'s Office<br>1106 Madison Street, Room 136<\\/p>\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"\"}}},\"4\":\"File a fictitious business name statement\"}}', '2016-02-10 21:49:17', '2016-02-10 21:49:17', '52968c82-1a58-4155-ad29-44b69232944e'),
 ('3322', '872', '3', '1', 'en_us', '9', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Obtain a Zoning Clearance Permit\",\"slug\":\"obtain-a-zoning-permit\",\"postDate\":1453931700,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"922\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>If you plan to operate a business in Oakland (including a home office), you will need to obtain a zoning permit called a&nbsp;<strong>Zoning Clearance<\\/strong>. You do not need a&nbsp;<strong>Zoning Clearance<\\/strong>&nbsp;if your business is located outside of Oakland or if your business activity is a rental property operator. The Zoning Clearance is granted if your business is allowed in the proposed location. In some instances, ahead of obtaining a Zoning Clearance, a proposed business activity must also go through a special&nbsp;<strong>Conditional Use Permit&nbsp;<\\/strong>process to determine whether the activity will be allowed.&nbsp;<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The Zoning Clearance is a one-time permit that is good as long as the nature of your business remains the same and in the same location. You will need this zoning permit before applying for your business tax certificate.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You may obtain additional information about zoning permits and regulations via the&nbsp;<strong>Zoning Hotline<\\/strong>&nbsp;(telephone), the&nbsp;<strong>Online Zoning Request Form<\\/strong>&nbsp;or by visiting the&nbsp;<strong>Permit Counter. Zoning Clearances<\\/strong>&nbsp;and other zoning permit applications are available online, but must be submitted and paid for in person at the Permit Counter.<\\/p>\",\"312\":{\"1522\":{\"type\":\"onlineLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"onlineTitle\":\"\",\"linkTitle\":\"Download the application\",\"linkUrl\":\"http:\\/\\/www2.oaklandnet.com\\/oakca1\\/groups\\/ceda\\/documents\\/agenda\\/oak040732.pdf\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"1\"}},\"1542\":{\"type\":\"physicalAddress\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"physicalAddressTitle\":\"Turning In Your Application In Person\",\"address\":\"<p><strong>Permit Counter<\\/strong><br>250 Frank H. Ogawa Plaza, Room 2114<br>Oakland, CA 94612<\\/p>\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"\"}}},\"4\":\"A zoning clearance permit is required if you plan to operate your business in Oakland\"}}', '2016-02-10 21:50:45', '2016-02-10 21:50:45', '35597ecd-4435-4725-a433-421ff495a222'),
 ('3332', '872', '3', '1', 'en_us', '10', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Obtain a Zoning Clearance Permit\",\"slug\":\"obtain-a-zoning-permit\",\"postDate\":1453931700,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"922\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>If you plan to operate a business in Oakland (including a home office), you will need to obtain a zoning permit called a&nbsp;<strong>Zoning Clearance<\\/strong>. You do not need a&nbsp;<strong>Zoning Clearance<\\/strong>&nbsp;if your business is located outside of Oakland or if your business activity is a rental property operator. The Zoning Clearance is granted if your business is allowed in the proposed location. In some instances, ahead of obtaining a Zoning Clearance, a proposed business activity must also go through a special&nbsp;<strong>Conditional Use Permit&nbsp;<\\/strong>process to determine whether the activity will be allowed.&nbsp;<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The Zoning Clearance is a one-time permit that is good as long as the nature of your business remains the same and in the same location. You will need this zoning permit before applying for your business tax certificate.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You may obtain additional information about zoning permits and regulations via the&nbsp;<strong>Zoning Hotline<\\/strong>&nbsp;(telephone), the&nbsp;<strong>Online Zoning Request Form<\\/strong>&nbsp;or by visiting the&nbsp;<strong>Permit Counter. Zoning Clearances<\\/strong>&nbsp;and other zoning permit applications are available online, but must be submitted and paid for in person at the Permit Counter.<\\/p>\",\"312\":{\"1522\":{\"type\":\"onlineLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"onlineTitle\":\"Download\",\"linkTitle\":\"Get the Zoning Clearance Form\",\"linkUrl\":\"http:\\/\\/www2.oaklandnet.com\\/oakca1\\/groups\\/ceda\\/documents\\/agenda\\/oak040732.pdf\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"1\"}},\"1542\":{\"type\":\"physicalAddress\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"physicalAddressTitle\":\"Turning In Your Application In Person\",\"address\":\"<p><strong>Permit Counter<\\/strong><br>250 Frank H. Ogawa Plaza, Room 2114<br>Oakland, CA 94612<\\/p>\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"\"}}},\"4\":\"A zoning clearance permit is required if you plan to operate your business in Oakland\"}}', '2016-02-10 21:51:27', '2016-02-10 21:51:27', '74314cda-84c7-4842-961d-15d6d153bdc3'),
 ('3342', '952', '3', '1', 'en_us', '25', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Obtain Your Business Tax Certificate\",\"slug\":\"obtain-your-business-license\",\"postDate\":1453934640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"922\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>Before you start, you will need your <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/beta.oaklandca.gov\\/services\\/businesses\\/start-your-business\\/register-your-business\\/obtain-a-zoning-permit#entry:872:url\\\">Zoning Clearance<\\/a> and <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/beta.oaklandca.gov\\/services\\/businesses\\/start-your-business\\/register-your-business\\/register-your-business-name#entry:942:url\\\">Fictitious Business Name<\\/a> applications approved.&nbsp;For more detail on&nbsp;exceptions on who needs a business tax certificate, click&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/beta.oaklandca.gov\\/#entry:2:url\\\"><\\/a><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/beta.oaklandca.gov\\/services\\/businesses\\/start-your-business\\/register-your-business\\/confirm-if-you-need-to-register-your-business#entry:1082:url\\\">here<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Cost<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The $88&nbsp;registration fee must be paid and filed within 30 days of starting your business.&nbsp; If you file your registration later than 30 days after you start your business, you will need to pay a small penalty plus interest for each month beyond the 30 days.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Application Process<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The New Business&nbsp;Application is available online&nbsp;and at our offices.&nbsp;You can pay by&nbsp;cash, check, cashier\'s check, money order,&nbsp;credit cards (Mastercard, Visa, & Discover),&nbsp;and ATM debit cards.&nbsp;However, if paying with an&nbsp;ATM&nbsp;debit card you must come into the office.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The application can&nbsp;be returned by fax (with a&nbsp;credit card), via mail or in person. If submitting by fax, you may pay by phone by&nbsp;provide the social security number or federal tax identification number on record.&nbsp;You will get a paper certificate from the business tax office approximately two weeks after you pay your fee.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Business Tax Office Hours<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Monday,&nbsp;Tuesday, Thursday, Friday&nbsp;8&nbsp;a.m.&nbsp;\\u2013&nbsp;4:00 p.m<br>Wednesday, 9:30 a.m. \\u2013 4:00 p.m<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Renewal<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Business taxes must be paid annually, on or before March 1st of each year. It is your responsibility to renew your certificate on time and\\/or to notify the Business Tax Office if you have not received your annual renewal declaration(s).<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<hr>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Non-Profit Registation<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>All non-profit organizations located or doing business in the City of Oakland are required to register with the city. To register as a non-profit, you must first have your 501(c)(3) from the&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.irs.gov\\/Charities-&-Non-Profits\\\">IRS<\\/a>, the Letter of Exemption from the&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.boe.ca.gov\\/info\\/VirtualSeminars\\/nonprofit_resources.html\\\">California State Franchise Board<\\/a>, a copy of your Articles of Incorporation, and, if you have a location in the City of Oakland, a zoning clearance for your business location (please contact the&nbsp;<u><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www2.oaklandnet.com\\/Government\\/o\\/PBN\\/OurOrganization\\/PlanningZoning\\/o\\/Zoning\\/index.htm\\\">Zoning Division<\\/a><\\/u>&nbsp;to obtain zoning clearance).&nbsp;Once you have obtained the above documents you must complete a&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.oaklandnet.com\\/government\\/fwawebsite\\/revenue\\/revenue_newbiaapp.htm\\\">Business Registration Application<\\/a>&nbsp;and provide the City with copies of your 501(c)(3), Letter of Exemption, and Articles of Incorporation.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>More Info<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Get the&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.oaklandnet.com\\/government\\/fwawebsite\\/revenue\\/revenue_biztax.htm\\\">business application (PDF), business tax classification and rate table, additional&nbsp;information, and FAQs<\\/a>&nbsp;on the City\'s Finance and Management Agency website.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Businesses located in or operating in Oakland need to pay an annual business tax on or before March 1 of each year.&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/oaklandbusinesscenter.com\\/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=37&Itemid=50\\\">See more details on the annual business tax here.<\\/a><br>&nbsp;<br><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/oaklandbusinesscenter.com\\/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=102&Itemid=85\\\">Visit the BAC or request help from the BAC online<\\/a>&nbsp;if you have additional questions or need more information.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<table><tbody><tr><\\/tr><\\/tbody><\\/table>\",\"312\":{\"1552\":{\"type\":\"onlineLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"onlineTitle\":\"Get the Form\",\"linkTitle\":\"Download the Business Tax Application\",\"linkUrl\":\"http:\\/\\/www2.oaklandnet.com\\/w\\/OAK046735\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"1\"}},\"1562\":{\"type\":\"physicalAddress\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"physicalAddressTitle\":\"In Person or By Mail\",\"address\":\"<p><strong>Business Tax Office<\\/strong><br>250 Frank H. Ogawa Plaza, Suite 1320<br>Oakland, CA 94612<\\/p>\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"\"}}},\"4\":\"To conduct any business in Oakland you must first obtain a Business Tax Certificate and pay an annual business tax\"}}', '2016-02-10 21:53:22', '2016-02-10 21:53:22', '94374bde-ebb7-422d-9daf-ba2fb53c82b9'),
 ('3352', '1092', '3', '1', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Check Your Building Plan\",\"slug\":\"check-your-building-plan\",\"postDate\":1454962860,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"1062\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>Once you have submitted all of your&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www2.oaklandnet.com\\/Government\\/o\\/PBN\\/OurServices\\/permits\\/index.htm\\\">required documents and building permit fees<\\/a>, our Building Services engineers will review your plans for&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www2.oaklandnet.com\\/Government\\/o\\/PBN\\/OurOrganization\\/BuildingServices\\/s\\/codes\\/index.htm\\\">compliance with applicable codes and regulations<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Plan check for new dwellings usually takes four to six weeks. However, plans with special engineering may take longer. Building Services will also submit your plans to the Fire Services agency for review. Fire review takes 1-10&nbsp;days.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>When you apply for your&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www2.oaklandnet.com\\/Government\\/o\\/PBN\\/OurServices\\/permits\\/index.htm\\\">Building Permit<\\/a>, Zoning staff will review the plans submitted to ensure that all conditions of approval are satisfied and that the plans are consistent with Zoning approval.&nbsp;If we return your plans to you for revision and resubmittal, plan check time will increase accordingly. For answers to your plan check questions, please call (510) 238-3891.<\\/p>\",\"312\":{\"1582\":{\"type\":\"phoneNumber\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"phoneNumberTitle\":\"Call Us for Assistance\",\"number\":\"1 (510) 238-3891\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"1\"}}},\"4\":\"\"}}', '2016-02-10 21:55:53', '2016-02-10 21:55:53', 'ef857d15-a242-40ff-8091-457fe86831b8'),
 ('3362', '1072', '3', '1', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Launching and Marketing Your Business\",\"slug\":\"lauching-and-marketing-your-business\",\"postDate\":1454715240,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"1362\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>There are a variety of marketing services and opportunities available to Oakland businesses.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Get Grand Opening Assistance<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The City of Oakland\'s Marketing department helps new businesses with press releases and events to announce their new businesses.&nbsp; Contact the Public Information Officer at 1&nbsp;(510)&nbsp;238-2107.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Oakland Grown<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The Oakland Grown campaign is Oakland\\u2019s campaign to encourage people to support locally-owned businesses and artists when they shop.&nbsp; Oakland businesses and artists that are locally-based and independently owned can get decals, listings on the Shop Oakland Grown website and other marketing benefits.&nbsp; Learn more on the&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/oaklandgrown.org\\/join.php\\\">Oakland Grown website<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Marketing Green Businesses<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Certified Green Businesses take advantage of the decals, website listings and other marketing that the Alameda County Green Business program does to promote green businesses. To become a green business and benefit from these marketing benefits, check out the&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.greenbiz.ca.gov\\/ShopGreenAC.html#legal\\\">Alameda County Green Business website<\\/a>. &nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\",\"312\":\"\",\"4\":\"The City provides a variety of services to help you market your business\"}}', '2016-02-10 21:56:41', '2016-02-10 21:56:41', '8cdea10f-6f30-4259-aac0-cfd881e98bc2'),
 ('3372', '132', '3', '1', 'en_us', '6', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Contest a Parking Ticket\",\"slug\":\"contest-a-parking-ticket\",\"postDate\":1450478580,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"122\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<h2>Contesting by fax, in person, or by mail<\\/h2><p><a href=\\\"\\\">Download and complete the <\\/a><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www2.oaklandnet.com\\/oakca1\\/groups\\/cityadministrator\\/documents\\/form\\/oak041670.pdf\\\">Contest Form<\\/a> or write a letter of explanation for contesting your citation.\\r\\nPlease include your name, address, telephone number, current mailing address and parking ticket citation number.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Keep a copy of your ticket for your records.\\r\\nReturn your Contest Form or letter, along with the original parking ticket and additional documents in Person, by Mail, or by Fax.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul><li>Please wait 48 hours from the time of issuance to ensure your citation is entered into the online system.<\\/li><li>It may take handwritten tickets up to two weeks to be entered into the online system.<\\/li><li>You must contest your ticket within 21 days of the date of issuance.<\\/li><li>You\\u2019ll need to upload up to three documents that provide evidence to support your written testimony.<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3 id=\\\"what-happens-next\\\">What Happens Next<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n  <li>The Parking Citation Assistance Center investigates your ticket.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>You will be notified of the decision by mail.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>If the ticket is upheld, you will have 21 days to pay your ticket or request an Administrative Hearing.<\\/li>\\r\\n  <li>If you contested a parking ticket and you are not satisfied with the decision, you can <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/beta.oaklandca.gov\\/services\\/parking\\/find-parking\\/request-an-administrative-hearing#entry:182:url\\\">request an Administrative Hearing<\\/a>.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ol>\",\"312\":{\"1402\":{\"type\":\"onlineLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"onlineTitle\":\"Online\",\"linkTitle\":\"Contest online\",\"linkUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/wmq.etimspayments.com\\/pbw\\/include\\/oakland\\/dispute_request.jsp.\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"1\"}},\"1412\":{\"type\":\"phoneNumber\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"phoneNumberTitle\":\"By Fax\",\"number\":\"(510) 986-2699\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"\"}},\"1422\":{\"type\":\"physicalAddress\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"physicalAddressTitle\":\"In Person or By Mail\",\"address\":\"<p><strong>Parking Citation Assistance Center<\\/strong><br>250 Frank H. Ogawa Plaza, Suite 6300<br>Oakland, CA 94612<\\/p>\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"\"}}},\"4\":\"\"}}', '2016-02-10 22:00:02', '2016-02-10 22:00:02', 'b74313a1-71a1-44b6-99fe-2b6eb2f37f11'),
