 ('942', 'field', '1', 'en_us', ' if you intend to name your firm anything other than your own name you must file a fictitious business name statement at the alameda county clerk s office this generally costs $30 you can download an application online pdf pick one up in person or have one mailed to you you may pay by cash debit atm check personal company bank cashier s or traveler s or money order ficitious business name applications info hours monday friday8 30 am 4 30 pm turning in your application by mail please be sure to send the original and 3 copies of the form and a self addressed stamped envelope to ensure a prompt return of your copies payment for additional certified copies are $2 00 per copy you may pay by check personal company bank or cashiers money order or traveler s checks out of country payments must be made in u s dollars credit cards are notaccepted for mail orders '),
