 ('222', 'field', '1', 'es', ' what to know do not attempt to drive your vehicle because severe damage may occur the parking boot program targets the most serious parking violators who have five 5 or more unpaid parking tickets a sticker will be displayed on a window of your vehicle showing that your vehicle has been booted this sticker will include instructions in english chinese and spanish phone assistance is available in multiple languages how to remove the boot from your vehicle pay the fines for the unpaid tickets you can make payments by phone or in person in most cases you can drive your vehicle in about five minutes payment plan options are available by phone pay the fines with a credit debit card or e check the operator will provide a six digit code this six digit code will allow removal of the boot without damage to your vehicle call the help center at 800 500 6484 if you need assistance with boot removal steps return the boot to the location provided by the help center in person pay the fines in cash you will receive a six digit code this six digit code will allow removal of the boot without damage to your vehicle call the help center if you need assistance with boot removal steps return the boot to the location provided by the parking assistance center hours mondays tuesdays thursdays and fridays from 9 a m to 4 30 p m wednesdays from 9 30 a m to 4 30 p m '),
